import { useContext } from 'react' import { Context } from '../../context' function PlanYear() { const { planChange, setPlanChange, setStepTwoCompleted, setPrice } = useContext(Context) const change = (event) => { setPlanChange(event.target.value) setStepTwoCompleted(true) if (event.target.value === 'Arcade') setPrice(9) if (event.target.value === 'Advanced') setPrice(12) if (event.target.value === 'Pro') setPrice(15) } return (
) } export { PlanYear }
